WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.233
Wu Qi

2
00:00:01.666 --> 00:00:04.766
Mu Yan's aunt has always been so outspoken

3
00:00:04.766 --> 00:00:06.100
Don't take it to heart

4
00:00:06.266 --> 00:00:07.100
But

5
00:00:07.333 --> 00:00:10.533
Although these dowry gifts you bring are extremely valuable

6
00:00:10.533 --> 00:00:14.066
But Mu Yan is our only daughter

7
00:00:14.166 --> 00:00:17.000
We have always regarded her as the apple of our eyes since we were children

8
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:19.066
But I understand what you mean.

9
00:00:19.366 --> 00:00:21.100
What else needs to be added to the list?

10
00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:22.666
You have the final say

11
00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:24.166
Blunt enough

12
00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:26.000
I'm not going around in circles then.

13
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.066
Tell the truth

14
00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:31.000
The investment of the group responsible for the accident has failed year after year

15
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:34.000
The funding hole is astronomical

16
00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:38.566
I'm afraid the 50 billion you funded is not enough.

17
00:00:38.566 --> 00:00:39.600
It's not hard

18
00:00:39.700 --> 00:00:41.200
I will definitely do my best.

19
00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:43.266
Help the Zhao family come back to life

20
00:00:43.566 --> 00:00:45.966
You can tell me the specific number.

21
00:00:45.966 --> 00:00:46.866
And

22
00:00:47.066 --> 00:00:51.133
Although our Zhao family used to be one of the four major families

23
00:00:51.133 --> 00:00:54.466
But you need to see other people's faces everywhere

24
00:00:54.700 --> 00:00:58.066
Now the Li Wang family has fallen

25
00:00:58.100 --> 00:01:00.533
Then I hope to take this opportunity

26
00:01:00.533 --> 00:01:03.733
Let the Zhao family become the largest family in Beihai

27
00:01:03.733 --> 00:01:06.400
After all, the North Sea is Great Xia's territory

28
00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:09.700
Even the Promise Palace cannot be exercised arbitrarily

29
00:01:10.166 --> 00:01:12.066
All over the world

30
00:01:12.300 --> 00:01:14.633
The Promise Temple overlooking all living beings

31
00:01:14.933 --> 00:01:16.833
Is there anything that can't be done?

32
00:01:17.666 --> 00:01:19.066
Hey, Sister Xiaowu

33
00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:21.300
Are you deliberately shirking?

34
00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:24.466
Don't forget that Mu Yan hasn't married you yet

35
00:01:24.466 --> 00:01:25.566
That being the case

36
00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:27.100
I will use all my connections

37
00:01:27.100 --> 00:01:29.266
I wish the Zhao family to climb to the top of the North Sea

38
00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:32.500
As expected of the Dianzu of Wuji Hall

39
00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:34.266
Sure enough

40
00:01:34.300 --> 00:01:37.566
But I have one last request.

41
00:01:37.566 --> 00:01:38.666
Uncle, but it doesn't matter

42
00:01:38.666 --> 00:01:41.000
I'll do my best no matter what.

43
00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:43.000
It's actually not a big deal

44
00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:45.166
You are the owner of the Promise Palace

45
00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.900
We Mu Yan are going to marry you soon

46
00:01:48.266 --> 00:01:51.266
Should this Wuji Temple be

47
00:01:51.566 --> 00:01:53.800
There is a share of our Zhao family

48
00:01:54.166 --> 00:01:55.666
Pardon me?

